      {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Differentiating term by term—"
      },
      {
        "type": "equation",
        "latex": "y = - 4 \\log \\left( a^{2} \\right) + a^{2} + 1 - \\log a + \\log a + a \\left( \\log a \\right)^{2} + 1 - \\log a + 2 \\log x + 2 \\log a + a^2 + 3.",
